{"tid":1470321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人準備好攬炒未？","createTime":"2019-08-14T04:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T05:09:40.000Z","uid":179144,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"627f0294c909a14bbddf97be257057397869d74c","tid":1470321,"uid":179144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:55:27.000Z","msg":"其實講到攬炒就真係低估咗中共<br />\n而係中共擺到明要搞鳩我哋香港<br />\n唔好以為香港要挾到佢，同一個無理性嘅人談何要挾？<br />\n<br />\n兩條路<br />\n一：我哋放棄or袋住先(<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />袋咗啲咩？)<br />\n大陸此仇必報，4千億唔會還，餘下嘅儲備用盡方法拎走埋，之後直接收香港皮打落2線城市，一國一制下正式唔再係國際城市<br />\n<br />\n二：我哋抗爭到底<br />\n大陸派人血洗，俾全球抵制，但香港從此失去國際金融中心嘅美譽，同時大陸就算要對抗外敵，都一定出招再大搞香港一獲<br />\n<br />\n無論點都好，中共班大佬呀家屬呀，都必定立晒所有錢走人，佢哋個個都有外國護照，真係理得個國家死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 準備好 炒佢老母<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔想呀 但有無方法"},{"pid":"d24f06b94ba805fe3a20e77460d059c9bf47803d","tid":1470321,"uid":179144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:55:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9590d8b028c004a517c58c79578131940eed0822","tid":1470321,"uid":179144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:57:27.000Z","msg":"炒佢老母"},{"pid":"5819ae922470551059e511099675543c4764918e","tid":1470321,"uid":179144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:58:18.000Z","msg":"利申 我唔想炒<br />\n我係唔係俾大陸攬炒"},{"pid":"7086f5b9f42050b6dcf32bbe267522047a4da3a7","tid":1470321,"uid":179144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:58:54.000Z","msg":"直接獨立啦"},{"pid":"178ae5c670d4351a67e978fdb1ff6ac6362ff9a5","tid":1470321,"uid":179144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:59:10.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"aad11fe576bd0ae9110c7c990db6b59395d0e8eb","tid":1470321,"uid":179144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:09:16.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"64b110cf485e7db3738eea0fbefd7372d484042f","tid":1470321,"uid":179144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:09:40.000Z","msg":"快啲脫離啦"}]}